  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD COMMUNITY</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/5481143b1e640ced8537aaea09616c46.avif?t=1774210187\" width=1295 height=183 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite Code: F9aRWT4sS4</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A GALAXY THAT WANTS YOU DEAD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on a chaotic, one-of-a-kind journey across the galaxy.</strong> Blast through handcrafted levels, face bosses who roast you every time you screw up, and survive a universe that absolutely wants you dead. Built by ex–League of Legends and Counter-Strike competitors, this game does <strong>not</strong> hold your hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your ship, chase leaderboard glory, and carve your name across the stars. If you’re looking for easy? Keep scrolling. If you want wild, fast, hilarious, punishing space combat... welcome aboard.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD YOUR SHIP. BREAK THE RULES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/a4272ae7535307d242d58ab525603d80.poster.avif?t=1774210187\" width=516 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/a4272ae7535307d242d58ab525603d80.webm?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/a4272ae7535307d242d58ab525603d80.mp4?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn credits, grab loot, and turn your tiny starter ship into a fully armed menace.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock weapons and mods</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reroll affixes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade gear to legendary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push broken, ridiculous builds that bend reality</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can imagine a build, you can probably break the game with it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PICK YOUR FRAME. MASTER YOUR STYLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/36619424ec8be39437c7fcc2fb0a6d65.poster.avif?t=1774210187\" width=516 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/36619424ec8be39437c7fcc2fb0a6d65.webm?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/36619424ec8be39437c7fcc2fb0a6d65.mp4?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from four unique Frames, each with its own skills, strengths, and playstyle:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attack Frame</strong> – Fast, vicious, and dual-wielding secondaries.<br><strong>Bomber Frame</strong> – Slow, tanky, obliterates entire screens.<br><strong>Engineer Frame</strong> – Drone support that heals, boosts DPS, or overwhelms enemies.<br><strong>Scout Frame</strong> – The fastest ship, creating deadly clones for constant pressure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your favorite... or master them all.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BOSSES WITH ATTITUDE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/ea9ee90f6d3ea70e499ab4c73b27a82d.poster.avif?t=1774210187\" width=512 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/ea9ee90f6d3ea70e499ab4c73b27a82d.webm?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/ea9ee90f6d3ea70e499ab4c73b27a82d.mp4?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for <strong>big, loud, over-the-top boss fights.</strong><br>These aren’t just giant enemies, they’re personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>They taunt you.</strong><br>They punish mistakes.<br>They push you to actually get good.<br>Beat them and walk away with massive loot drops and bragging rights.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHAOS IS BETTER WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.poster.avif?t=1774210187\" width=516 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.webm?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.mp4?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo <strong>or team up</strong> with up to <strong>4 players</strong>.<br>Coordinate builds, revive each other, stack synergy weapons, and take on challenges that feel impossible alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More players = more loot, more chaos, more screaming.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS BOUNTIES. ENDLESS BRAGGING RIGHTS.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the Campaign, dive into the <strong>Bounty System</strong>. A brutally scaling endgame ladder with global leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level ramps:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New variants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bigger rewards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb as high as you can before the galaxy crushes you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO HAND-HOLDING. NO MERCY. JUST PURE ACTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, challenging, hilarious, and unapologetic.<br>A bullet-hell ARPG made by competitive players, for players who want real stakes, real chaos, and real satisfaction when they win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re ready to earn your victories, pilot get in the cockpit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
