e personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>They taunt you.</strong><br>They punish mistakes.<br>They push you to actually get good.<br>Beat them and walk away with massive loot drops and bragging rights.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHAOS IS BETTER WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.poster.avif?t=1774210187\" width=516 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.webm?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108250/extras/7eee3a9a647c44689ef97ce2bf45ca98.mp4?t=1774210187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo <strong>or team up</strong> with up to <strong>4 players</strong>.<br>Coordinate builds, revive each other, stack synergy weapons, and take on challenges that feel impossible alone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More players = more loot, more chaos, more screaming.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS BOUNTIES. ENDLESS BRAGGING RIGHTS.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After the Campaign, dive into the <strong>Bounty System</strong>. A brutally scaling endgame ladder with global leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level ramps:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy damage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemy health</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New variants</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bigger rewards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb as high as you can before the galaxy crushes you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO HAND-HOLDING. NO MERCY. JUST PURE ACTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast, challenging, hilarious, and unapologetic.<br>A bullet-hell ARPG made by competitive players, for players who want real stakes, real chaos, and real satisfaction when they win.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re ready to earn your victories, pilot get in the cockpit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
